title: Administração Interview
Application Type: I applied online. The process took 2 days. I interviewed at Jessie Trice Community Health Center (Salvador, Bahia) in Jan 2021
Interview Descriptions: Uma empresa boa para trabalhar , comunicação boa com a equipe, empresa organizada de grande porte .Empresa agradável, ambiente tranquilos, ótimos benefícios, mas poucas áreas e chances de crescimento.Tive a oportunidade de aplicar minha experiencia na area comercial e fui contratada com exito pela excelente gerente na época.Aprimorei minha experiência na gestão de equipes e processos para atendimento consultivo,televendas
Interview Questions: Quais o seu ponto fraco e forte e seu objetivo

title: Job Coach Interview
Application Type: I applied online. The process took 5 days. I interviewed at Jessie Trice Community Health Center (New York, NY) in Jan 2019
Interview Descriptions: It was laid back. I felt comfy. I wore my best clothes. I was really interested in this job. I knew that I needed to impress them if I wanted the job

title: Purchasing Clerk Interview
Application Type: I applied online. The process took 1 week. I interviewed at Jessie Trice Community Health Center (Miami, FL) in May 2017
Interview Descriptions: Scripted interview includes HR and manager of the department. Was asked questions concerning knowledge of the department and the position.  No discussion of pay. Manager went on a tangent saying how impressed he was with my interview but didn't hire me.
Interview Questions: What do you think a purchasing clerk does?
